{"type": "article", "id": 5118, "title": "可变U型枕的围巾 Clay", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-12T07:55:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233805Wotd908l6BxgXbNC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是 clay 原创家居工作室推出的一款多用途产品，集合了围巾、U型枕与披肩 3 种功能于一身，非常适用于经常出差或旅行的人。不管是在开足了冷气的车厢，还是长途飞行会经历温差很大的两地，clay 都可以提供临时性的保暖功能，重要的是还要很有型。当然，旅途中需要小憩的话，Clay 还能够卷成 U型枕的样子。提供灰色与藏青色两种选择，售价 238 元，<a href=\"http://hi.taobao.com/market/hi/detail2014.php?spm=a215p.1472517.a31cp.1.MYuqdE&amp;id=6617#\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233803MpbdeLNzRDatY9qs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.528125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233803eCDniuE7rMXIcxKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052338049gHDBPm5tYOTb1KS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233804X0mt6n4C2icwHhsk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233805Hr4T3ugmwO6ifXsc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}